imdb.plot outline: If you're a fan of Korean drama, do not miss this year-end show. The "SBS Drama Awards" which celebrates the best dramas and comedians of the year, according to the large Korean network. Since 1993, every year on December 31, the SBS Drama Awards is part of the SBS Awards, which includes the SBS Entertainment Awards and the SBS K-pop Awards.
